cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

This paper is about keyphrase extraction, which is a task related to information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, keyphrase extraction can be approached as a machine learning problem, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and deep learning (cs.DL).
